# core

Motor Python do Spindle: validação, metadados e download via yt-dlp.

## Layers
- `domain` — entities, errors, ports
- `application` — GetVideoInfo, DownloadMedia
- `infrastructure` — YtDlpVideoGateway, URL/path validators
- `bridge` — NDJSON stdio para o Electron
- `cli` — download_youtube

## Entry
- Bridge: `python -m core.bridge.stdio_server`
- CLI: `python download_youtube.py` (raiz) ou `python -m core.cli.download_youtube`
- Freeze Windows: `packaging/spindle_core_main.py` → `spindle-core.exe`

## Conventions
- Use cases orquestram validators + gateway
- Somente hosts YouTube; `noplaylist`
- Sem UI; sem Pillow/thumbnail no hot path do bridge
- `SPINDLE_FFMPEG` / `FFMPEG_LOCATION` apontam ffmpeg embutido no app empacotado
